data.description: Beautiful two story home located in the Poet Square subdivision on Evansville's north side. When entering this home you step into a spacious foyer with hardwood floors that flow throughout the first floor. The large living area opens up to the dining room and beautiful kitchen. The Kitchen has beautiful granite counters, stainless steel appliances, a large pantry, an island that offers lots of extra cooking space. There is a 1/2 bath on the main level for added convenience. You will enjoy the over sized master suite located on the upper level, with three additional bedrooms and another full bathroom. The open bonus space is  on the upper level will make a great conversation space.  The laundry area is located on the upper level as well. This property has a shared pond and a two car attached  garage.
